&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drives ARR expansion&lt;/strong&gt; by consistently meeting and exceeding monthly, quarterly, and annual revenue targets across new and existing client portfolios within the APAC territory.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Executes SaaS solution selling&lt;/strong&gt; strategies, converting complex financial prospects into long-term partners using impactful value-based framework techniques.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Generates and manages a robust sales pipeline&lt;/strong&gt;, independently qualifying new opportunities through targeted outbound execution, personal networks, and regional partner channels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Orchestrates active deal cycles&lt;/strong&gt;, meticulously managing a pipeline

